				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="dablink">For other people named Douglas Adams, see <a href="Douglas_Adams_(disambiguation)" title="Douglas Adams (disambiguation)">Douglas Adams (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
